<H1>Debian Goes International</H1>

<HR>

<P>This page contains links to versions of documentation in specific
languages. It is hoped that all Debian documentation will be translated to
every language and be available directly in the Debian web site. Until that
happens this page contains links to documentation on other sites that may be
of use to Debian users worldwide.

<P>The Debian web site uses <A href="cn">content negotiation</A> to
automatically deliver web pages in your preferred language - if your browser
is configured properly and a page exists in that language. We have created a
page that explains <A href="cn">how to set up the preferred language for
your browser</A>.</P>

