<H2><A name="Chinese">Chinese</A></H2>
   <UL>
   <LI>Debian Chinese users/developers mailing list.
      To subscribe send a message to
      <A href="mailto:debian-chinese-REQUEST@lists.debian.org">debian-chinese-REQUEST@lists.debian.org</A>
      with the word "subscribe" as the subject.
   <LI>A preliminary home page for the <EM>Debian Chinese Project</EM> is available
      at
      <A href="http://www.debian.org/~foka/debian/chinese/">http://www.debian.org/~foka/debian/chinese/</A>.
      (Pick index.zh-cn.html for GB code; index.zh-tw.html for Big5 code.)
      A slightly less updated version is at 
      <A href="http://www.debian.org/chinese/">http://www.debian.org/chinese/</A>.
   </UL>

